    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个“Express <i>汽车清洗模拟器</i>”序章版本中，你可以体验核心游戏机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>清洗、打泡、放松。享受令人满意的体验。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开始清洗吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单直观的机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-立即开始行动- </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种颜色的肥皂清洗汽车……赏心悦目！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集卡片，迎接新顾客！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从小型轿车到大型SUV甚至卡车，清洗各种车辆并获得报酬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>信任还是麻烦？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些顾客看起来人畜无害……但别被欺骗，每个人都有可能藏着秘密。交出钥匙前要三思：信任可能带来利润，也可能带来麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的风格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用各种有趣的贴纸装饰每一辆车：增添个性、风格，甚至一点混乱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用彩色肥皂清洗汽车！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受色彩鲜艳的泡沫带来的满足感！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关心你的顾客！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了满足顾客，才能保持生意兴隆！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>他们的快乐就是你的“财”福！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> </p><br>",
